name: manifest
description: Free yourself from the life you have for the life you want. Most people settle, trapped in cycles they didn’t choose, repeating the same days over and over. Manifest is the break, a bold decision to rewrite your reality, to step into the version of you that chases more, demands more, becomes more, and refuses to settle. It’s not luck. It’s choice. It’s action. It’s time to truly manifest your future.
